Pre-Game Insights: Devin Booker returned to the lineup for Tuesday night's game against Memphis after missing five games with a left groin strain.
Suns starting center Jusuf Nurkic is out while serving the second game of a three-game suspension for his involvement in a fight.
Ja Morant is out indefinitely with a right shoulder strain for the Grizzlies, and rookie center Zach Edey is sidelined while in concussion protocol.
